title: Episode 369: Trophy or Starfish? (Feat. Kidd Kenn)
itunes:title: Episode 369: Trophy or Starfish? (Feat. Kidd Kenn)
description:
Rapper, Kidd Kenn joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his latest EP "Grown." Kidd Kenn opens up about why he's never been in a relationship before, introducing boys to his mom, being a starfish in bed, and much more. Kidd Kenn even challenges the ladies to a d*** sucking contest! Enjoy!
